data.text:
Many congratulations on qualifying for Dean’s List in the Spring 2024 semester, an accomplishment that points to your many academic talents. This honor is awarded to full-time undergraduates who earn a grade point average of at least 3.4 during the university’s fall and spring semesters. This spring’s Dean’s list students represent 39 states and 34 foreign countries.

While my colleagues and I firmly believe that students’ pathways are much more than a series of courses, semesters, and grades, we are just delighted that you were able to achieve such a high level of performance. Your resilience impresses us all.

With best wishes, and with hopes that your achievement this semester will impact your own trajectory, at Furman and beyond, in meaningful ways.
